targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  lending_rates.time,
  lending_rates.venue || ':' || lending_rates.token AS text,
  lending_rates.rate * 24 * 365 * 100 AS rate
FROM lending_rates
WHERE
  lending_rates.venue IN ($venue)
  AND lending_rates.token IN ($token)
ORDER BY lending_rates.time

SELECT
  lending_rates.time,
  lending_rates.venue || ':' || lending_rates.token AS text,
  lending_rates.rate * 24 * 365 * 100 AS positive_apr_rate
FROM lending_rates
  LEFT JOIN products ON products.base = lending_rates.base AND products.quote = lending_rates.quote AND products.venue = lending_rates.venue AND products.type = 'spot'
  LEFT JOIN tokens ON tokens.symbol = products.base
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(lending_rates.time)
  AND products.base IN($token)
  AND lending_rates.rate >= 0
ORDER BY time ASC, positive_apr_rate DESC

SELECT
  lending_rates.time,
  lending_rates.venue || ':' || lending_rates.token AS text,
  lending_rates.rate * 24 * 365 * 100 AS negative_apr_rate
FROM lending_rates
  LEFT JOIN products ON products.base = lending_rates.base AND products.quote = lending_rates.quote AND products.venue = lending_rates.venue AND products.type = 'spot'
  LEFT JOIN tokens ON tokens.symbol = products.base
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(lending_rates.time)
  AND products.base IN($token)
  AND lending_rates.rate < 0
ORDER BY time ASC, negative_apr_rate DESC

SELECT
  predicted_funding_rates.next_funding_time AS time,
  predicted_funding_rates.venue || ':' || product AS text,
  predicted_funding_rates.next_funding_rate * 24 * 365 * 100 AS rate
FROM predicted_funding_rates
  LEFT JOIN products ON products.symbol = predicted_funding_rates.product AND products.venue = predicted_funding_rates.venue AND products.type = 'swap'
  LEFT JOIN tokens ON tokens.symbol = products.base
WHERE
  predicted_funding_rates.next_funding_time > DATE_TRUNC('hour', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
  AND products.base IN($base)
ORDER BY time, rate DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  NOW() - interval '4 hours' AS time,
  venue || ':' || token AS text,
  AVG(rate) * 24 * 365 * 100 AS rate
FROM lending_rates
WHERE
  time >= NOW() - interval '4 hours'
  AND token = 'usd'
GROUP BY venue, token
